      in
        ISZERO ⟫ ELSE (⟦ k with-var m₁ with-fyi m₂ ⟧¹ᵉ ⟫ return m₁ n)
  ⟦ caseₒ p a b ⟧²ᵉ =
    ⟦ p ⟧⁰ᵉ ⟫ ELSE ⟦ b ⟧²ᵉ ⟫ ⟦ a ⟧²ᵉ

  open Sⁿ    using (S²)
  open Sⁿ→Oⁿ using (⟦_⟧²)

  S²→Oᴱ : ∀ {Guy Act ease}
        → (Guy → Addrᴱ)
        → (Act → String)
        → S² Guy Act ease → Oᴱ
