  O²→Oᴱ : O² Addrᴱ String → Oᴱ
  O²→Oᴱ x = prelude ⟫ ⟦ x ⟧²ᵉ ⟫ REVERT

  compile : ∀ {ease} → S² Addrᴱ String ease → Oᴱ
  compile = S²→Oᴱ (λ x → x) (λ x → x)


